title: Group Therapy: Does She Tell HR?
description: Shyla called in for Group Therapy this week and she's a little upset about her co workers not acknowledging her goal of being able to cross her legs now that she's lost weight. They don't see it as an issue and she's not sure how to procced. Should she tell HR? Confront them? Or do nothing?
